\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 manipulative - please others as a way to soothe our own system. Gaining concern or care}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 self image - negative self appraisal}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 violence - self directed}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 empathy - low cognitive empathy high affective empathy - cant discern how someone is feeling but sure is trying to express and react to it.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 they dont lash out, but very good at ghosting - disappearing from peoples lives.}
